This project is made possible using software components with the following license terms.

	- Only the components that you use are relevent to projects using SxE.

	- You can likely stuff a copy of this in your games manual or some sort
	  of "Help -> About" notice in your UI.

	- You probably should include this complete text (or relevent portions)
	  in the EULA phase of your games installer, if applicable
	  (e.g.  Windows, probably; Android, probably not).

	- SxE's own terms are provided in the COPYING file. You should include that too ;).

