==> scripting/rhino <==

Rhino is used unmodified as a possible backend for the scripting module. You do
not need to use the scripting module to use SxE or Rhino for a JavaScript
backend, both are provided as continence.

Source code can be found at https://developer.mozilla.org/en/RhinoDownload and
https://github.com/mozilla/rhino -- refer to scripting/rhino/build.gradle for
the version used. At this time of writing, it is version: '1.7R4'.

For frequently asked questions, please see http://www.mozilla.org/MPL/2.0/FAQ.html.

